9740   // not exceed max unsigned value of this type), this effectively proves
9741   // that there is no wrap during the iteration. To prove that there is no
9742   // signed/unsigned wrap, we need to check that
9743   // Start <= Last for step = 1 or Start >= Last for step = -1.
